## ğŸ”„ Migration from Other Systems

### From "Camera Roll" style:
```bash
# Move dated files to monthly folders
for file in Shortform/*.mp4; do
    month=$(date -r "$file" +%Y-%m)
    mkdir -p "Shortform/Archive/$month"
    mv "$file" "Shortform/Archive/$month/"
done
```

### From "All in One Folder":
```bash
# Organize by platform (if filename contains platform)
grep -l "tiktok" * | xargs -I {} mv {} TikTok/
grep -l "reel" * | xargs -I {} mv {} Reels/
```

---

**Shortform content needs different organization than long-form. Choose the strategy that fits your use case!**

